00:17:01,358 --> 00:17:03,557
He deliberately said something else

332
00:17:03,558 --> 00:17:08,457
so that you wouldn't just agree to what he said.

333
00:17:08,458 --> 00:17:10,057
I'm sorry.

334
00:17:10,058 --> 00:17:12,557
Oh no.

335
00:17:12,558 --> 00:17:16,558
Which means that Asao is, Asao is...

336
00:17:19,658 --> 00:17:22,657
At any rate, let's hurry and call the police.

