340
00:17:35,358 --> 00:17:36,557
What?

341
00:17:36,558 --> 00:17:40,657
Strange, I used this phone just a while ago.

342
00:17:40,658 --> 00:17:43,257
Do you have any other phones or a spare cable?

343
00:17:43,258 --> 00:17:45,057
This is the only phone

344
00:17:45,058 --> 00:17:47,757
